                  <p><b>Self-help books</b> provide guidance, advice, and strategies for personal development and self-improvement. They cover topics like motivation, goal-setting, mindfulness, relationships, and overcoming challenges, aiming to empower individuals to enhance their well-being and achieve their goals. With practical exercises and inspiring anecdotes, self-help books offer tools and insights to foster personal growth, boost resilience, and create positive change in one's life.</p>
